Class PodcastImage

java.lang.Object
com.apptasticsoftware.rssreader.module.podcast.PodcastImage
public class PodcastImage extends Object
Represents a podcast image that allows for delivering images of various sizes and use cases. This class is cross-compatible with the <itunes:image> tag but expands the use cases for delivering more than just square channel or episode art.
